race.description: Magic Millions Jan Yearling Sale Super Mdn Handicap
race.comment: Tough race to end the day. TOUSSAINT (6) holding her form and comes back a few levels for this fifth-up. Went out quickly and tired badly in the straight when fifth over 1600m at Randwick. Earlier runs had merit and expected to go close today. LEGO MASTER (4) total forgive from the wide gate on debut when a battling sixth over 1400m at Orange. Much better than that and no shock to see him take this out. LAPIS LAZULI (3) extra trip in her favour and has the figures to take a hand in the finish. PROISARYA (12) debuts and warrants a market watch. MILLY MOLLY MANDY (15) has placed in her past two outings. Will give them all something to chase.
